methods.clear: Release all resources held by the cache.
methods.createPlaceholder:
Attempt to instantiate an instance of valueType with the nullary constructor, in order to create a placeholder
 instance reference.

Note: Java generics information - <VALUE_TYPE>

:param valueType: (java.lang.Class<VALUE_TYPE>) - The type of the desired placeholder
:return: (VALUE_TYPE) A placeholder instance reference
methods.get:
Lookup the value for index.

:param index: (int) - The offset (must be >= 0)
:param extra: OffsetLookupCache.EXTRA_INPUT_TYPE
:return: (OffsetLookupCache.VALUE_TYPE) The result of calling the lookup function for index, possibly from cache

text: Caching data structure interface for caching int (offset) to Object mappings.
